query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(it mi t ci) NoHashJoin(ci it mi t rt) NoMergeJoin(ci it mi rt t mc) NoHashJoin(ci it mc mi rt t cn) NoHashJoin(ci cn it mc mi rt t n) NoHashJoin(ci cn it mc mi n rt t an) NoHashJoin(an ci cn it mc mi n rt t chn) */ select min(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
min(t.title) AS jap_engl_voiced_movie
from info_type AS it
inner join movie_info AS mi
on it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)',
'(as Jewel)')
inner join role_type AS rt
on rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress'
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f'
inner join aka_name AS an
on ci.person_id = an.person_id AND n.id = an.person_id
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id;
